  "title": "ISic003023. Rupestral graffiti describing sexual relations",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: <a href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/UQRFDXEG\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/UQRFDXEG</a></div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"aba\">section a</span>  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"diva--interpretive\">  <a id=\"aa-l1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Νυμφόδωρος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Νυμφόδωρος\">Νυμφόδωρος</span></span> κεχαρισμένα[ν] figure, zoomorphic ταριχ[ο]πώλας <br id=\"aa-l2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>[ἐ]πύγιζε <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Δάμυλιν\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Δάμυλιν\">Δάμυλιν</span></span>  </span></div>  <span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"abb\">section b</span>  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"divb--interpretive\">  <a id=\"ab-l1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Δάμυλις\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Δάμυλις\">Δάμυλις</span></span> ἁ κεχαρισμένα <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Νυμφοδώρου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Νυμφοδώρου\">Νυμφοδώρου</span></span> γυνὰ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: <a href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/UQRFDXEG\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/UQRFDXEG</a></div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"aba\">section a</span><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"diva--diplomatic\"><a id=\"aa-l1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Νυμφόδωρος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Νυμφόδωρος\">ΝΥΜΦΟΔΩΡΟΣ</span></span>ΚΕΧΑΡΙΣΜΕΝΑ[.]figure, zoomorphicΤΑΡΙΧ[.]ΠΩΛΑΣ<br id=\"aa-l2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>[.]ΠΥΓΙΖΕ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Δάμυλιν\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Δάμυλιν\">ΔΑΜΥΛΙΝ</span></span></span></div><span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"abb\">section b</span><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"divb--diplomatic\"><a id=\"ab-l1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Δάμυλις\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Δάμυλις\">ΔΑΜΥΛΙΣ</span></span>ΑΚΕΧΑΡΙΣΜΕΝΑ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Νυμφοδώρου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Νυμφοδώρου\">ΝΥΜΦΟΔΩΡΟΥ</span></span>ΓΥΝΑ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text of Manganaro</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag</a></p>  <p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>The texts record sexual acts between Nymphodoros, a seller of salted fish, and Damylis.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 42.0850 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a></li><li> Manganaro 1992 492-497, no. VII figs. 30-36 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001830\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001830</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"><p>Standard quadrate Greek letters of the Hellenistic period.</p> Line 1-2  60-80  Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
